# Canonical site URL for SEO (canonical links, Open Graph, JSON-LD). Defaults to https://relliahealth.com if unset.
# VITE_SITE_URL=https://relliahealth.com

# Optional: override Sanity project (defaults match website-cms/sanity.config.ts)
# VITE_SANITY_PROJECT_ID=
# VITE_SANITY_DATASET=production
#
# Sanity content is fetched read-only from the browser; failed queries fall back to shared/cms/defaults.
# For draft/preview or private datasets, use a server-side fetch or a read token — never expose write tokens in Vite env.
#
# useMarketingPage(slug) + marketingPage documents: wired in code but no dedicated route yet — add a route when needed.

# Diagnostics report generation (server-only; never use VITE_* for secrets)
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Stripe Payment Links for /payment (monthly vs annual). If unset, client falls back to a default buy.stripe.com URL.
# VITE_STRIPE_MONTHLY_PLAN_LINK=https://buy.stripe.com/...
# VITE_STRIPE_ANNUAL_PLAN_LINK=https://buy.stripe.com/...

# QMS program detail (/programs/qms) — optional override for hero + pricing CTAs.
# Other programs will get their own env keys or rely on Sanity per-program paymentUrl as cards grow.
# VITE_QMS_PAYMENT_LINK=https://buy.stripe.com/...
